@node "HISTORY" "hISTORY"

                                    @{b}@{u}History@{ub}@{uu}

 Hundreds of BETA-releases were tested by sCANDiC!
 Thousands of changes have been made to the program...

Vers.  Date
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1.31 (12.04.96) - Nuke-messy's will now be 'Private'.
                  suggestion by Enzo.

1.2  (10.16.96) - Fixed a stupid Bug: dCN!Nuke also updated the 
                  dCN!Top-Datafiles, when giving a User credits for his upload.
                  reported by Enzo.

1.1  (10.14.96) - Extended Funktion: dCN!Nuke updates now dCN!Top-Datafiles
                  when nuking some bytes from an User.
                  Extremly needed by Enzo.

1.0  (10.08.96) - first public Release-version.

0.96 (10.08.96) - Bugfix: Files where deleted, even when selecting to give
                  Credits for Uploader, instead of only taking Credits!

0.95 (10.07.96) - Rewritten the Up/Downloader search routine! It's now
                  incredible fucking fast!

0.9  (10.04.96) - Changed the Design, and added Cursor-Key Control.

0.8  (10.01.96) - Added Wildcard-Option.

0.7  (09.25.96) - Added: dCN!NukeLog.FIM for faster Nuking Actions.

0.3  (09.01.96) - Simple Nuker. No special features.

@endnode

